movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: The Worst 'A' Film in History?
review: While I try to think of a worse major movie, let's list the five most idiotic aspects of the film:#5 The Ben-Hur scene#4 The Spartacus scene#3 Jar-Jar Binks#2 Vader is Jesus#1 Darth Maul is really a bad guy because he has horns
